This lab demonstrated real-world File Integrity Monitoring using Wazuh. It reinforced SOC analyst skills in alert triage, risk assessment, and incident response decision-making. The exercise highlights the importance of monitoring critical system files and maintaining strict visibility over authentication-related configurations.

